{"tid":484100,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每到深夜 總會想起一個人","createTime":"2017-11-29T18:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T15:37:21.000Z","uid":12360,"like":235,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc7abc82f44daed30cd10ada94811373c5aa315","tid":484100,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T18:57:44.000Z","msg":"呢個人可能係你前度 曖昧對象 鍾意過既人 甚至係一位過客<br />\n佢地可能係你生命中佔左一段唔長既時間 但卻可以令你每晚牽掛<br />\n或者依家你同佢再冇聯絡 就算有都冇咩計傾<br />\n但諗返起果陣同佢傾計既時光令你既嘴角都會自動上揚<br />\n有時候你都會想關心下佢既近況 但又怕打亂佢既生活<br />\n天氣轉涼果陣你會諗起佢既壞習慣而想去提醒佢<br />\n或許大家都係一個冇資格再關心佢既人<br />\n但其實大家心裡面都仲會好掛住佢<br />\n都係想同佢講返句 凍啦 著多件衫 小心冷親<br />\n代每一位掛念的人 送出問候 乾杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"025376b1a675e1720bc29ff63b88d2daf7326d8f","tid":484100,"uid":12360,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T19:15:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">可能你會見到呢個post<br />\n我欠你一句對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"128dffff909ce78fabaf600b9dd490e0b0d088bc","tid":484100,"uid":12360,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"又一晚了 <br />\n今晚好熱 但唔好著太少 冷風然在 小心冷親<br />\n代各位再次送上問候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423a1295741cd1fc6577647ca1cf5261677846d8","tid":484100,"uid":35763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bd591ee0926433ad4268881fc5f9ebd5d75750","tid":484100,"uid":12360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:48:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n訓唔著既話<br />\n不如係到留低你想講既野等個人舒服d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d40492afe75806da4458a66e49291acde87f58","tid":484100,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"我要同佢講：其實我好鐘意你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a3c130c34a3268a2ca9b7afe9b41185c6d46dd","tid":484100,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"但唔知點開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a8d473efff02de6ef56883e40d6d5a3e3b49b8","tid":484100,"uid":137618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"我好掛住你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddb57cd0c1eb042837720f374ffd0dea43fff9a","tid":484100,"uid":68258,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0b945ff32fbc6fbf4866e2588a80e17d3ecd89","tid":484100,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:23:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但唔知點開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接開口 痛痛快快咁了結件事<br />\n做男人既唔好拖泥帶水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938e8a32ead474b234bd7236037b04735be7fb11","tid":484100,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:24:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就讓我代佢同你道歉<br />\n對唔住"},{"pid":"3dab7fe9b53ce190617c670ddfaed03c34896760","tid":484100,"uid":66173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:25:41.000Z","msg":"講埋哂啲咁general既野 但又句句中！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf92b4d9bb95cbd099fffae5dd71c54824a1211","tid":484100,"uid":133090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:29:56.000Z","msg":"同佢生活咗2年，分開咗23日。前日見佢病咗希望佢快啲好番。"},{"pid":"3a72201e78d7c5c10633818e6d846c710eb996b9","tid":484100,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講埋哂啲咁general既野 但又句句中！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n過獎了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbbfa385a27777d58d0975d10d53fb78719ebe4","tid":484100,"uid":12360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢生活咗2年，分開咗23日。前日見佢病咗希望佢快啲好番。</blockquote><br />\n雖然一句善意既關心係好易<br />\n但怕再同佢拉上關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853d4c8207d1432b2b2a217e06befa139105f385","tid":484100,"uid":137851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:33:42.000Z","msg":"我哋做翻朋友好嗎？<br />\n妳比我繼續留喺你身邊好嗎？<br />\n妳比我照顧妳好嗎？"},{"pid":"e45a0503157867522d972f9446f94341b7dd0df4","tid":484100,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:35:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我哋做翻朋友好嗎？<br />\n妳比我繼續留喺你身邊好嗎？<br />\n妳比我照顧妳好嗎？</blockquote><br />\n有想法既下一步就係行動<br />\n或許佢同你有共同既諗法<br />\n但大家就係只差踩出既一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f6c134da60a75d798eddd865f854d2c53e3999","tid":484100,"uid":44201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:36:30.000Z","msg":"見到佢又俾人針對 又俾人踩 好想幫佢擋晒啲箭 但諗起我已經乜嘢資格都冇 個心嘅傷口又介深咗"},{"pid":"f27eeb7657dd98b0ae6efce8aa5cafcc4830610f","tid":484100,"uid":160772,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:43:54.000Z","msg":"分左手又復合最後都係分手 <br />\n雖然到而家重好吾甘心 <br />\n但每次一個人好失落嘅時候都只會諗起你 <br />\n差唔多半年了 <br />\n你最近還好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386080d25d11a56a0a76a965f833b8ed6d2feb67","tid":484100,"uid":157107,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fb38c7e7e1c0df9f97fad94b19f9bba48ba5a9","tid":484100,"uid":29059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T19:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手又復合最後都係分手 <br />\n雖然到而家重好吾甘心 <br />\n但每次一個人好失落嘅時候都只會諗起你 <br />\n差唔多半年了 <br />\n你最近還好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吾你老母"},{"pid":"ac8791d1fa2eab286da8475b58df24031233ba63","tid":484100,"uid":104063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T20:05:24.000Z","msg":"其實我真係唔介意你嘅過去 <br />\n點解你仲係要咁介懷自己以前d野 <br />\n我想你同返我一齊生活可以過得好d 無咁大壓力<br />\n即使依家你未準備好 我都會等你 係你身邊陪伴住你"},{"pid":"2b71911694def6abc19a3e89f82772759b752db7","tid":484100,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T15:36:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27d4b2c00c027220212c13c8134eb5d1c1d40707","tid":484100,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:12:07.000Z","msg":"又一晚啦<br />\n今晚返風啦 著多件衫啦<br />\n仲有廿幾日聖誕啦 唔知你會點過呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f5c5badae572490ec9fb4cf8b55886c4ee5cb6","tid":484100,"uid":40742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdabe2f010fa08470fb3c00a18b687ab7186b68","tid":484100,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11885fc9a29749437f86ca99ef522bf55bfa952b","tid":484100,"uid":134220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s